      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Tough to split this lot. EXPLICABLE (1) raced close to the lead before clearing out to score a convincing win over this track and trip last time. Should be right there again. GUSMAO (3) has been in the money at his last couple of runs, the latest when second behind GUSMAO 12 days ago. Meets her with a good pull at the weights with the 2kg claimer going on and should be at his top now. Great chance to turn the tables. FOOTPRINTS (2) bounced back last start and landed the prize as favourite here. Tougher for her this time but anticipating another big run. HOLDER MAID (5) was a dominant all the way winner here two back but failed to go on with it at Bordertown last time. Capable of bouncing back sharply back on the dirt.",
